snippet.title: Amber Johnson popularly known as @Ammberlynne is an American model and social media personality.
snippet.description:
#Melanin Mottos I live by, I’m not sure if you heard of this before, but they say “shoot for the stars and if you miss you’ll land amongst the moon”. 

Amber Johnson popularly known as @Ammberlynne is an American model and social media personality. 
The amazing brown skinned beauty has had incredible success with her social media by posting pictures and videos of her modeling exploits.
She has a Tiktok following of 355 thousand subscribers.
Amassing over 5 million likes.

The fashion model has an Instagram following of 91 thousand followers.
The beauty resides in Inglewood California. 
Tikstar ranks her as the 314.121st most popular TokTok personality in the United States 
She is a brand ambassador for Hot grl Clothing brand and is heavily featured on the companies social media pages

She also reps from OhPolly a woman owned swimwear company , she has an incredible bikini body herself.

And shoppbecanne the fashion retailer 
 
Amber: I think it always is very important to keep a level head. For me, I like to keep things very balanced. So if I do need to take breaks from social media, I will take it. Because if you’re not balanced you won’t appreciate everything that’s going on in the moment. Because you’re so caught up on “how to keep growing”, “how to not lose that growth” and such. I think it’s very important to take breaks and balance yourself.
